---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About – Efficient CTO"
  description="Learn about Mehmet, a fractional CTO with 20+ years of experience helping startups build scalable technology."
>
  <Header />

  <main>
    <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem; color:var(--color-navy); margin-top:3rem;">
      About Efficient CTO
    </h1>

    <p style="max-width:700px; margin-top:1rem; color:#475569;">
      Efficient CTO was founded to help startups and growing businesses make smarter technical decisions,
      build scalable products, and accelerate engineering execution — without the cost of a full-time CTO.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin-top:3rem; color:var(--color-navy);">Experience</h2>
    <ul style="line-height:1.7; color:#475569;">
      <li>20+ years in software engineering</li>
      <li>Leadership roles in startups and enterprise companies</li>
      <li>Architecture, product strategy, and engineering management</li>
      <li>AI consulting and automation strategy</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="margin-top:3rem; color:var(--color-navy);">Leadership Philosophy</h2>
    <p style="max-width:700px; color:#475569;">
      Technology should accelerate business outcomes — not slow them down. My approach blends strategic
      clarity with hands-on execution, helping founders move faster with confidence.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin-top:3rem; color:var(--color-navy);">Mission</h2>
    <p style="max-width:700px; color:#475569;">
      To empower founders and teams with the technical leadership they need to build great products,
      scale efficiently, and avoid costly mistakes.
    </p>

    <CTA />
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
